DECIMAL (10 digits --> 0 to 9)

any number ^ 0 =1
any number ^ 1 = any number

56 = 50 + 6
    = (5 x 10^1) + (6 x 10^0)
    = 50 + 6
    = 56

123 = (1 x 10^2) + (2 x 10^1) + (3 x 10^0)
    = 100+20+3
    = 123


HEXADECIMAL (16 digits --> 0 -9 & A -10,B-11,C-12,D-13,E-14,F-15)
AD = (A x 16^1) + (D x 16^0)
   = (10 x 16) + (13*1) 160 + 13 
